{"tid":1993023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[將軍澳斬人案］有目擊者清楚睇晒成個過程 不過警察無搵佢錄口供同叫佢做證人","createTime":"2020-04-28T13:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T02:01:13.000Z","uid":22556,"like":77,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"a9f5b3e94c4f8c56f8270fc0c3c584304ee8a3bb","tid":1993023,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:10:45.000Z","msg":"作為目擊者，閱畢將軍澳洪震斬人案判詞。好多人討論郭法官如何形容社會運動；如何形容洪震；跳躍邏輯推演&mdash;&mdash;我不重複，但我想講兩個判詞與事實相榷之處：<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n我抵達隧道時，洪震已經開始斬人。我於坑口入口目睹洪震斬人時，有一位男士用木梯阻擋洪震。隨後我大聲喝止洪震，洪震轉身走向我，並係坑口出口用刀指向我。我留意到刀型比較利（相信係牛肉刀，見判詞），應該係斬向其他受害者嘅同一把刀。<br />\n<br />\n而當時地上已經有另一把刀（長方形狀，相信係菜刀，見判詞）。另一把「未經使用」嘅刀點解會係地？<br />\n<br />\n我怕我記錯，於是搵返當日新聞&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n香港01（見文末link）：<br />\n期後，該名男士突然表示，「我忍唔住啦」，從身後拿出「西瓜刀」襲擊友人，「揮刀失控」。徐稱，自己曾嘗試用梯阻擋還擊，將對方手持的「西瓜刀」擊落地，但此料不及對方再拿起另一把菜刀，徐再從附近拿單車抵擋，對方才逃離現場，其後更曾到區內屋苑嘉明閣更衣以便逃離。<br />\n<br />\n可見不論刀型，洪震都係用一把刀企圖攻擊失敗，然後用另一把刀施襲。<br />\n<br />\n原本一把刀施襲還是兩把刀施襲，雖是案情部份，但非最重要。在我理解中，單刀與雙刀唔會影響施襲本質，但判詞第91段：「再者, 即使被告開始襲擊3名受害人, 但他從來沒有使用第二把刀。如果他早有意圖襲擊受害人等並且帶著兩把刀, 當他展開襲擊時, 他就沒有理由不拿出所有武器。」<br />\n<br />\n我唔知點解有呢個邏輯，但如果一把刀同兩把刀有「意圖」上嘅分別，我可以話：「係兩把。」<br />\n我見到，目擊證人徐先生見到。<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n判詞第87段：「他們對很多基礎建設例如地鐵肆意破壞。」案發當日係2019年8月20日凌晨。地鐵被破壞，係8月31日之後出現，根本唔係洪震犯案時背景同社會實況。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n連結<br />\n<br />\n判詞：<br />\n<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=127566&amp;QS=%2B&amp;TP=JU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fsearch%2Fsearch_result_detail_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D127566%26QS%3D%252B%26TP%3DJU&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=7748b41f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=127566&amp;QS=%2B&amp;TP=JU</a><br />\n<br />\n當日新聞 <br />\n香港01：<br />\n將軍澳連儂牆斬人案　傷者友人質疑組織性預謀：佢先係真正暴徒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/361702/%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86%E6%96%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%A1%88-%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E6%80%A7%E9%A0%90%E8%AC%80-%E4%BD%A2%E5%85%88%E4%BF%82%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F361702%2F%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2584%2582%25E7%2589%2586%25E6%2596%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%2582%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%258F%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E6%2580%25A7%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25AC%2580-%25E4%25BD%25A2%25E5%2585%2588%25E4%25BF%2582%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25BE%2592&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=0b4407ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/361702/%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86%E6%96%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%A1%88-%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E6%80%A7%E9%A0%90%E8%AC%80-%E4%BD%A2%E5%85%88%E4%BF%82%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92</a><br />\n<br />\n伸延閱讀 <br />\n關鍵評論網：<br />\n將軍澳連儂隧道斬人案，郭偉健法官判辭導賞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/134377?fbclid=IwAR3lU5PQupCuMFryVNVUypuzhCwUGTjrgt8E9ex9K4x58NUDOPgWcV_8QIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F134377%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3lU5PQupCuMFryVNVUypuzhCwUGTjrgt8E9ex9K4x58NUDOPgWcV_8QIs&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=256949d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/134377?fbclid=IwAR3lU5PQupCuMFryVNVUypuzhCwUGTjrgt8E9ex9K4x58NUDOPgWcV_8QIs</a><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 唔記得講，洪震持刀向我，趨前至3米距離左右我只能轉身跑，中途叫一對情侶唔好行去隧道；然後求其上左剛剛到站，往旺角方向N293，係寶琳落車再返現場，並同警員講我係目擊證人。留低聯絡後，警員話現場證人好多，有需要會聯絡我。之後就無人聯絡過我。講真，當時我都覺得呢件事係我人生中告一段落。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/865080416/posts/10163192644975417/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F865080416%2Fposts%2F10163192644975417%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=f6a3eb69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/865080416/posts/10163192644975417/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"8bc2e8369e96b3d4c45270d3d5d37dd4a1b4cef4","tid":1993023,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:40:50.000Z","msg":"無人理😅"},{"pid":"46d56d68d975ad0a96801c6c20f7800b8f2451f4","tid":1993023,"uid":261895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:44:22.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1852f8e78f82c2d6a6ef4806d5ca5b2f04f5f0cf","tid":1993023,"uid":27388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:48:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc12d842f6de0325fbf4fc1fd34f6a3d85f70e64","tid":1993023,"uid":34047,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:48:32.000Z","msg":"呢單案有冇得重審<br />\n根本係意圖謀殺<br />\n有哂準備<br />\n早一星期已話要斬人"},{"pid":"55f9cf80bb23fee1a0cea169d47b5513c74e4e8a","tid":1993023,"uid":45508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:51:44.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"74234cf8dea3f591fa4309aaf5568454ce6fc4a4","tid":1993023,"uid":138382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:52:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37e67326276247be1398fb3f883216cca5c58a6b","tid":1993023,"uid":138382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:52:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9f3d532f19adce4b0c14796f7475c1b7932f787","tid":1993023,"uid":138382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2