s://lih.kg/1979496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1979496</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n（預言）九東立會必敗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1976827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1976827</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n因爲熱血都話要參加初選，所以你更加要簽呢個聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1975432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1975432</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n新東初選：點解「素人反而更堅持限制名單」？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1973926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1973926</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n仲記得帝怡/環保北/盛福/都善/大白田西/愛俊/龍城發生咩事嘅，全部同我入黎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1972316\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1972316</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n攬炒時光機之時空旅行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1970812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1970812</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n(請廣傳)立法會初選與三不投聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1967776\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1967776</a><br />\n<br />\n（緊急）「攬炒藝術家」：聯署要人！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1966811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1966811</a><br />\n<br />\n【堅。找數真漢子】呢個聯署過一百萬簽名我裸跑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1955200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1955200</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會選舉就到啦，我哋有咩可以做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1968274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1968274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3cdaa2235ef6703604f38977db01c649c7b3feb7","tid":1993023,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8f2fcd9124048f1d36294eb089f44f1c674bb9","tid":1993023,"uid":234944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:25:36.000Z","msg":"PUSH!!"},{"pid":"57d9c377a10efbbb196ab480e70ee09839d12607","tid":1993023,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT